 </svg><strong>60W maximum:</strong> Standard USB-C cable (3A, no E-Marker)</li>
 <li><svg class="icon-check text-green-500 mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
 <path d="M434.8 70.1c14.3 10.4 17.5 30.4 7.1 44.7l-256 352c-5.5 7.6-14 12.3-23.4 13.1s-18.5-2.7-25.1-9.3l-128-128c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l101.5 101.5 234-321.7c10.4-14.3 30.4-17.5 44.7-7.1z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg><strong>100W maximum:</strong> 5A cable with E-Marker required</li>
 <li><svg class="icon-check text-green-500 mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
 <path d="M434.8 70.1c14.3 10.4 17.5 30.4 7.1 44.7l-256 352c-5.5 7.6-14 12.3-23.4 13.1s-18.5-2.7-25.1-9.3l-128-128c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l101.5 101.5 234-321.7c10.4-14.3 30.4-17.5 44.7-7.1z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg><strong>240W maximum:</strong> EPR cable with E-Marker required</li>
 </ul>
 </div>
 
 <div class="bg-brandBlue rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8">
 <h3 class="text-xl font-black uppercase italic mb-4"><svg class="icon-shield-halved text-brandOrange mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
